<div style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px;">
            where c is the hypotenuse (longest side)
        </div>
<p></p></div>
<div class=3D"pitagoras-quiz-exercise">
<h4 class=3D"pitagoras-quiz-exercise-title">Exercise 1: Find the Hypotenuse=
</h4>
<div class=3D"pitagoras-quiz-problem">
<p>A right triangle has legs of 3 cm and 4 cm.</p>
<p>How long is the hypotenuse?</p>
<div class=3D"pitagoras-quiz-triangle-diagram">
